{"type": "article", "id": 25936, "title": "Skechers 一季度大涨，以及， 阿迪达斯未来特辑很不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-04-25T10:47:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2355, "name": "眼镜"}, {"id": 6579, "name": "春夏系列"}, {"id": 4867, "name": "首尔"}, {"id": 141, "name": "展览"}, {"id": 190, "name": "时装秀"}, {"id": 11440, "name": "睫毛膏"}, {"id": 1258, "name": "YSL"}, {"id": 9725, "name": "Skechers"}, {"id": 10258, "name": "Estée Lauder"}, {"id": 2002, "name": "Balmain"}, {"id": 18474, "name": "Free people"}, {"id": 26700, "name": "Dolce& Gabbana"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703120800PkrQh6y14zmxiptb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Skechers-achieves-record-revenues-in-Q1-2016,685591.html#rc\"><b>Skechers 一季度业绩良好</b></a>｜Skechers 近日发布公司截至 2016 年 3 月 31 日的一季度财报，收益将近 10 亿美元。净销售额从去年同期的 7.68 亿美元，上涨了 27.4% 至 9.788 亿美元，净收益也从 5610 万美元增至 9760 万。其 COO 兼 CFO David Weinberg 表示 Skechers 的产品需求有显著增长，他表示为了满足增长的需求，投资基础设施，包括提高欧洲配销中心的效率。<br></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Estee-Lauder-makes-more-key-appointments,685798.html#.Vx1t54QrJQY\"><b>雅诗兰黛任命更多新高管</b></a>｜雅诗兰黛（Estée Lauder）最近宣布 Damon Burrell  和 Anna Klein 分别担任消费者互动部门高级副总裁和公司事务部副总裁，旨在扩大公司消费者参与和提高数字能力，继续强化全球企业传播。Burell 于今年 4 月 11 日加入公司，此前在 Nickelodeon 影业担任全渠道营销高级副总裁。Anna 则将在 7 月 1 日上任新职位，从 2007 年起她就负责全球通信部门的增长。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/robb-report-launches-u-k-edition-10414196/\"><b>《罗博报告》推出英国版</b></a>｜关于高消费阶层生活方式的杂志 《罗博报告》（<i>Robb Report</i>）近日发布英国版，包括纸质与线上，涉及商业、汽车、文化、珠宝、食物、腕表等等方面。148 页的首刊将突出一份针对英国“无阶级富人”新贵的财富报告等内容。前 <i>Times Luxx</i> 编辑 James Collard 担任主编。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/-Balmain-stages-archive-exhibition-in-Seoul,685519.html#.Vx1t_IQrJQY\"><b>Balmain 首尔办展</b></a>｜现任创意总监 Olivier Rousteing 带领下，Balmain 在首尔办展，首先在 Arumjigi  楼的展示包括 2016 年春夏系列的走秀和之后的 party。展示之后，这个馆藏展览将在乐天世界塔持续展出至 5 月 19 日。展览探索并突出品牌背后的历史，展出最具代表性的系列，包括 Pierre Balmain 的 1946 年秋冬系列。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Hong-Kong-expects-May-1-holiday-tour-groups-from-China-to-decline-by-half,685261.html#.Vx1134QrJQY\"><b>大陆赴港旅行团数量五一预计将减半</b></a>｜受到海外及周边跨境游的影响，对于即将到来的五一劳动节小长假，赴港的大陆旅行团数量预计将减半。香港的旅游业协会的执行理事 Joseph Tung 表示旅行团数量过去几个月已经减少了 40%－50%，呈现缓和的趋势，对于即将来临的劳动节，“我们可能会看到与去年同期相比下跌了 40%－50% 的局面，比如一天 150 团。”去年同期一天为 300 团。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Adidas Originals 为其 NMD 和 Tubular 春夏系列<a href=\"http://bae.hypebeast.com/2016/4/adidas-originals-nmd-tubular-2016-spring-summer-lookbooks-zanna-roberts-rassi?utm_source=InternalHBtoHBae&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=InternalHBtoHBaelinks\">拍摄了一组未来特辑</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120741VkrAljChO7E6ZInL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120742fUvxs8da3wJzIN4Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120742A05xyvMP3rF1Vh72.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120742AYwLrlW5p2RFTeXv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120743ftwLys8moqTZADnB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120743A6EGz0Tbs5cqZFH1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120744436m0sOnldpDukvf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120744GVMrgYhawOZfCeWy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.purseblog.com/tory-burch/new-tory-burch-robinson-collection/\">Tory Burch 推出春季新款 Robinson  系列包袋</a>。<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120745YVXPJBIULSsj0NDn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120745WwXjR591SD2qCdT4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031207467K6UvmGjnf2SYFBc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120746t2VMeK3CfRxohDkl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031207479yXvk7dwECZfBVK4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120747WpRPrntfS0LCsQaM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/13428892/ysl-vinyl-couture-colored-mascara-lloyd-simmonds-cara-delevingne/\">YSL 将推出一个系列的彩色睫毛膏</a>，这个  Vinyl Couture 系列包含蓝、粉、金、银等九个颜色，预计 29 美元一支，五月上市：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312074823cYOyfu7GwEFKHj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48863636\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">刚刚过去的地球日，3.1 Phillip Lim 联合著名艺术家、环保主义者林璎（Maya Lin）推出一个呼吁环保行为的有机棉系列，名为<a href=\"http://bae.hypebeast.com/2016/4/3-1-phillip-lim-earth-day-capsule\">\"What Is Missing?\" </a>：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312074835mlRk19KXQeu4T8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120749hDrxISdP7l2aAuKp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120749iKY4CP31DaomNe0y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120750HhG2esBQTqSilgEu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"> Nordstrom 百货拍摄了一组  Free People 品牌的<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/free-people-festival-outfit-ideas-2016/\">时尚潮流特辑</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120750s9cdHRw6VnIFOolA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78947368\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120751WfrXyUs4h9A5lnIV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78947368\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120751zRe05F8Dkwrh9fSL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78947368\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120752tXZzyAwgkCWsflco.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120752trDLE85TfAuQJSNW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120754jqciavztHkTndrfl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120754cQL4AEjGh9UpJ8nZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/dolce-gabbana-eyewear-spring-2016-campaign/\">Dolce &amp; Gabbana 2016 春夏眼镜系列大片出炉</a>，满眼热情洋溢的西西里岛风情印花和停不下来的自拍梗：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120755VrjYKSClhNPef9To.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031207569OAb1VkKDuCZsElW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031207560AazsvylLDmXxdbK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031207575mljQ23yZSnV7CPf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120757cGOKil185nbpPIzf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120758cBGEZQv5jmNtH0Vx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Nigo 为自己的品牌 HUMAN MADE 推出手机指环支架，在自己的<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BEh2JiqEes5/\"> Instagram 上发布消息</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120759U3vSFYTIlHbN0Keu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58988159\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}